title: There's A Mystery In Studio That Only Bert Can Solve
description:
Yesterday, Kristin had a few questions for us. One of the questions was directed to Bert about a picture he used for a TikTok challenge we did. He was supposed to use photo's of the cast, but he went rouge and googled a random image.
But there's something strange about this image, and now we have a mystery to solve!
